         does not change        

03:08.354 --> 03:10.757
    the specific information    
         you were given.        

03:10.823 --> 03:12.592
     I guess I just meant--     

03:12.659 --> 03:14.160
         -You gotta keep        
      your facts straight.      

03:14.194 --> 03:15.395
             Hey...             

03:15.428 --> 03:16.663
       This guy's a liar!       

03:16.696 --> 03:17.764
             Oh...!             

03:17.830 --> 03:19.499
