17:18.837 --> 17:20.439
             -Mm-hm.            
  I know that wasn't Charlotte. 

17:20.506 --> 17:23.175
  -Yeah, and she's also making  
 this really weird ringing noise

17:23.208 --> 17:25.511
    that's stuck in my head.    
    Can you tell her to stop?   

17:25.544 --> 17:27.112
     It's really distracting    
         for all of us.         

17:27.179 --> 17:28.714
       Leia, is that you?       

17:28.747 --> 17:30.449
              Huh?              

17:30.516 --> 17:32.184
  REPORTER: [TV] ...by a child. 

17:32.217 --> 17:33.786
        Excuse me, ma'am,       
         what happened?         

17:33.852 --> 17:35.888
        It was that kid!        
       He Home Aloned me!       

17:35.921 --> 17:38.690
      That kid's a psycho!      
        Everything hurts!       

17:38.724 --> 17:40.893
 REPORTER: And what do you mean 
      he "Home Aloned" you?     

17:40.926 --> 17:43.062
           Look at me!          
   He gave me the works, okay?  

17:43.095 --> 17:45.898
  Torched door, Micro Machines, 
     paint can to the face,     

17:45.931 --> 17:47.733
     paint can to the nuts,     
        it wouldn't stop!       

17:47.766 --> 17:49.234
      -But how do you know      
         the assailant?         

17:49.268 --> 17:51.570
    His parents are in Paris    
     again and they asked me    

17:51.603 --> 17:54.706
to check in on him, but I didn't
  know he was a little psycho!  

17:54.740 --> 17:57.976
That little reptile has no soul!
          Cold-blooded!         

17:58.043 --> 18:00.913
     Leia, did a preteen boy    
         boobytrap you?         

18:00.946 --> 18:03.715
               Oh!              
         That's not me.         

18:03.749 --> 18:05.551
     I think that's actually    
       Jennifer Lawrence.       

18:05.584 --> 18:07.152
  That's not Jennifer Lawrence. 

18:07.219 --> 18:09.288
  -That's definitely you, Leia. 
            -Really?            

18:09.321 --> 18:10.722
 'Cause now that you mention it,

18:10.756 --> 18:12.591
    I think that looks a lot    
     like Jennifer Lawrence.    

18:12.624 --> 18:13.559
    You're missing a tooth...   

18:13.592 --> 18:15.094
              What?             
             Where?!            

18:15.127 --> 18:17.429
       [under her breath]       
 My gold tooth-- I'll kill him! 

18:17.463 --> 18:19.798
   REPORTER: My producers have  
   informed me that we do have  

18:19.832 --> 18:21.567
    the home security footage   
     of the incident, but...    

18:21.600 --> 18:23.068
            Come on,            
      don't show the video.     

18:23.102 --> 18:24.336
 REPORTER: ...viewer discretion 
           is advised.          

18:24.403 --> 18:26.638
     [cartoon sound effects]    

18:26.672 --> 18:28.173
            [laughs]            

18:28.240 --> 18:29.241
       [exaggerated boom]       

18:29.274 --> 18:30.576
           [laughter]           

18:30.609 --> 18:32.511
     Okay, the sound effects    
       do make it funny...      

18:32.578 --> 18:33.812
         Sorry I'm late.        

18:33.846 --> 18:35.481
         Crazy weekend.         

18:35.514 --> 18:37.116
         Oh, hey, J-Law?        

18:37.149 --> 18:38.650
           I love her.          

18:38.684 --> 18:40.752
            [coughs]            
              Ugh!              

18:40.786 --> 18:44.022
                ♪               

18:45.591 --> 18:46.758
   ANNOUNCER: [robotic voice]   
        Hello, everyone.        

18:46.792 --> 18:48.594
          It's time for         
    the Half Time Dance Cam.    

18:48.627 --> 18:51.797
 Football fans, get on your feet
                               !

18:51.830 --> 18:53.966
           Nice moves!          

18:53.999 --> 18:56.335
           Nice moves!          

18:56.368 --> 18:57.769
    Oh, what do we have here?   

18:57.803 --> 19:00.639
     Looks like she doesn't     
        want to move it.        

19:00.672 --> 19:02.174
            Come on,            
  the Dance Cam has found you!  

19:02.207 --> 19:04.443
       You gotta move it!       

19:04.476 --> 19:06.178
       Come on, everyone,       
  give her some encouragement!  

19:06.211 --> 19:07.513
         [crowd cheers]         

19:07.546 --> 19:10.616
     ANNOUNCER: There we go.    
              Yeah!             

19:12.184 --> 19:15.187
           That's it.           
           Got for it!          

19:15.220 --> 19:17.556
        [crowd cheering]        

19:17.623 --> 19:19.791
 EXECUTIVE: Are you seeing this?

19:19.825 --> 19:21.894
     EXECUTIVE 2: Of course     
        I'm seeing this.        

19:21.960 --> 19:23.695
      It's everything that      
     we've been looking for.    

19:23.729 --> 19:25.397
                ♪               

19:25.464 --> 19:29.668
 EXECUTIVE 2: Quirky, adorable, 
    beautiful, charismatic...   

19:29.701 --> 19:31.703
                ♪               

19:31.737 --> 19:34.506
       I can't look away.       

19:34.540 --> 19:36.842
      That is the new face      
        of our franchise.       

19:36.875 --> 19:39.144
         Yeah, more like        
     chest of our franchise!    

19:39.178 --> 19:41.547
       -Come on, grow up.       
             -Sorry.            

19:41.580 --> 19:43.582
        [crowd cheering]        

19:43.649 --> 19:45.651
     What do you think, sir?    

19:45.684 --> 19:48.754
           I think...           

19:48.820 --> 19:52.024
         A star is born!        

19:52.057 --> 19:54.059
              Yes!              

19:54.092 --> 19:57.896
        [crowd cheering]        

19:57.930 --> 20:00.566
      [inspirational music]     

20:00.599 --> 20:04.036
     [distant traffic noise]    

20:04.069 --> 20:07.105
                ♪               

20:07.172 --> 20:09.908
                ♪               

20:09.942 --> 20:13.278
                ♪               

20:13.345 --> 20:17.182
                ♪               

20:17.216 --> 20:20.219
  One day I'll catch my break.  

20:20.252 --> 20:24.089
          [radio plays          
     upbeat indie pop song]     

20:24.122 --> 20:29.928
                ♪               

20:29.962 --> 20:31.463
                ♪               

20:31.530 --> 20:36.702
           ♪ I met you          
       at the wrong time ♪      

20:36.735 --> 20:41.807
  ♪ Fireworks like 4th of July ♪

20:41.873 --> 20:45.811
         ♪ Stars were out       
       shinin' so bright ♪      

20:45.877 --> 20:48.046
  (What the fuck was I thinking)

20:48.080 --> 20:51.883
     ♪ It was like the blind    
       leading the blind ♪      

20:51.917 --> 20:56.555
                               ♪

